---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import CTASection from '../../components/ui/CTASection.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../../components/ui/Breadcrumbs.astro';
import TestimonialsSection from '../../components/sections/TestimonialsSection.astro';

const city = "Rutherford";
const title = "CPA in Rutherford NJ | Tax & Accounting Services | ProAxis";
const description = "ProAxis provides expert CPA services in Rutherford NJ — hospitality and restaurant accounting, retail tax planning, NYC commuter returns, and bookkeeping. 100% virtual.";
const canonical = "/service-areas/rutherford/";
const breadcrumbs = [
  { name: "Service Areas", url: "/service-areas/" },
  { name: city }
];
const schema = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": ["LocalBusiness", "AccountingService"],
  "name": "ProAxis Tax & Accounting Services",
  "telephone": "+12018002330",
  "email": "info@proaxiscpa.com",
  "url": "https://www.proaxiscpa.com",
  "address": {
    "@type": "PostalAddress",
    "addressLocality": "Hasbrouck Heights",
    "addressRegion": "NJ",
    "postalCode": "07604",
    "addressCountry": "US"
  },
  "areaServed": { "@type": "City", "name": "Rutherford, NJ" }
};
---

<BaseLayout {title} {description} {canonical} {schema} {breadcrumbs}>
  <Breadcrumbs items={breadcrumbs} />

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1C1C1E 0%, #2E75B6 100%);" class="py-14 lg:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold mb-4" style="background-color: rgba(197,165,90,0.2); color: #C5A55A;">
        Serving {city}, NJ &bull; 100% Virtual
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold font-heading text-white mb-4">CPA &amp; Accounting Services in {city}, NJ</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-8">ProAxis delivers expert tax preparation, tax planning, bookkeeping, and business advisory to {city} businesses and residents — all virtually, all on your schedule.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <a href="/contact/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-7 py-3.5 rounded-lg font-semibold text-white" style="background-color: #22C55E;">Schedule Free Consultation</a>
        <a href="tel:+12018002330" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-7 py-3.5 rounded-lg font-semibold text-white border-2 border-white/40">Call (201) 800-2330</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 lg:py-16">

    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold font-heading mb-5" style="color: #1C1C1E;">Rutherford's Business &amp; Community Landscape</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Rutherford is a charming borough in the southern Bergen County tier, distinguished by its lively Park Avenue downtown district, its strong literary legacy — the poet William Carlos Williams was born here and practiced medicine in Rutherford for most of his life — and its strategic location in the commercial shadow of the Meadowlands Sports Complex. The borough combines the character of an established residential community with a genuinely active street-level commercial life along Park Avenue, making it one of southern Bergen County's most livable and economically interesting boroughs.</p>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">The Meadowlands Sports Complex — home to MetLife Stadium, the Meadowlands Racing &amp; Entertainment complex, and, just to the south, the American Dream mega-mall in East Rutherford — is the single most powerful economic driver in the immediate region. When the New York Giants and New York Jets play home games, when major concerts fill MetLife Stadium's 82,000 seats, or when major events draw tens of thousands of visitors to the Meadowlands area, the economic activity radiates outward through Rutherford and its immediate neighbors. Hospitality businesses, restaurants, bars, parking operations, transportation services, and catering companies in the Rutherford area benefit significantly from Meadowlands traffic — but managing the boom-bust revenue patterns of event-driven businesses requires accounting systems and financial planning that can handle highly variable cash flows.</p>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Park Avenue in downtown Rutherford is one of southern Bergen County's most successful independent commercial districts. The street hosts a mix of independent restaurants, specialty retail shops, wine and spirits stores, professional service offices, nail salons, barber shops, and the kind of eclectic retail mix that attracts foot traffic from both Rutherford's own residents and visitors from neighboring communities. Many Park Avenue businesses are owner-operated, which means the business's financial results flow directly to the owner's personal tax return — creating the need for integrated business and personal tax planning that a proactive CPA provides year-round, not just at filing time.</p>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Rutherford has excellent NJ Transit rail service — the Boonton Line serves Rutherford with direct trains to New York Penn Station, making it a natural community for Manhattan commuters who want Bergen County's lower cost of living with convenient city access. This commuter population contributes NYC-connected complexity to the borough's tax landscape: New York nonresident income tax filings, the NJ credit for taxes paid to NY, and in some cases, the nuances of New York's convenience-of-the-employer rule for remote workers whose companies are based in Manhattan.</p>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-8">The Route 3 and NJ Turnpike corridors near Rutherford support significant commercial and industrial activity — warehousing, logistics, automotive businesses, and commercial real estate investment. Commercial property owners along these corridors manage significant asset values with complex depreciation schedules, CAM charges, and lease structures that have direct tax implications. ProAxis works with commercial real estate owners throughout southern Bergen County to optimize the tax treatment of their property portfolios.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold font-heading mb-5" style="color: #1C1C1E;">Tax &amp; Accounting Needs in Rutherford</h2>
    <ul class="list-none space-y-3 mb-6">
      {[
        { heading: "Hospitality and restaurant accounting", text: "Restaurants, bars, and catering businesses near the Meadowlands face specific accounting challenges: tip reporting and FICA obligations, NJ meals and sales tax, food and beverage inventory management, and the cash-intensive nature of many hospitality operations." },
        { heading: "Event-driven business cash flow planning", text: "Businesses whose revenue spikes around Meadowlands events need financial planning that accounts for variable cash flows — building reserves during peak periods and managing operating costs during slower months." },
        { heading: "Independent retail bookkeeping", text: "Park Avenue's independent retailers benefit from clean QuickBooks or Xero bookkeeping, accurate NJ sales tax tracking, inventory management, and monthly financial reports that give owners real-time visibility." },
        { heading: "NYC commuter tax planning", text: "Rutherford residents commuting to Manhattan need coordinated NJ and NY state tax returns, proper work-from-home day allocation, and the benefit of the NJ credit for taxes paid to New York." },
        { heading: "Commercial real estate tax strategy", text: "Property owners along Route 3 and the Turnpike corridor benefit from proper depreciation scheduling, cost segregation analysis on industrial and commercial properties, and capital gains planning on eventual property sales." },
      ].map((item) => (
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 rounded-lg" style="background-color: #F7F8FA;">
          <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0" style="background-color: #C5A55A;"></div>
          <div><span class="font-semibold" style="color: #1C1C1E;">{item.heading}:</span> <span class="text-gray-700">{item.text}</span></div>
        </li>
      ))}
    </ul>

    <!-- ProAxis Services -->
    <div class="rounded-2xl p-8 mb-10" style="background-color: #F7F8FA;">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold font-heading mb-5" style="color: #1C1C1E;">ProAxis Serves Rutherford Businesses &amp; Residents</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-5">From Meadowlands-adjacent hospitality businesses to Park Avenue retailers to NYC commuters, ProAxis delivers expert CPA services to Rutherford's diverse business and residential community through our fully virtual delivery model.</p>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
        {[
          { name: "Tax Preparation", link: "/tax-services/tax-preparation/" },
          { name: "Tax Planning", link: "/tax-services/tax-planning/" },
          { name: "Bookkeeping", link: "/business-services/bookkeeping/" },
          { name: "Business Advisory", link: "/business-services/" },
          { name: "NJ SALT Consulting", link: "/tax-services/nj-salt-consulting/" },
          { name: "Fractional CFO", link: "/business-services/fractional-cfo/" },
        ].map((svc) => (
          <a href={svc.link} class="flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2.5 rounded-lg bg-white border border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-300 font-medium transition-all" style="color: #2E75B6;">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
            </svg>
            {svc.name}
          </a>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold font-heading mb-5" style="color: #1C1C1E;">Why Choose a Virtual CPA in Rutherford</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Rutherford's Park Avenue business owners are busy running their shops, kitchens, and service businesses. ProAxis's virtual model means they get expert accounting support without losing a morning to a CPA appointment. Our cloud-based systems integrate with modern point-of-sale and accounting platforms, making the data flow from your business to your CPA team seamless.</p>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">Based in neighboring Hasbrouck Heights, ProAxis knows southern Bergen County — its commercial character, its tax issues, its business community — from the inside. We're not a national chain that's never been to the Meadowlands.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold font-heading mb-5" style="color: #1C1C1E;">Nearby Areas We Also Serve</h2>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mb-8">
      {[
        { name: "Hasbrouck Heights", slug: "hasbrouck-heights" },
        { name: "Garfield", slug: "garfield" },
        { name: "Hackensack", slug: "hackensack" },
        { name: "Bergen County (all)", slug: "bergen-county" },
      ].map((area) => (
        <a href={`/service-areas/${area.slug}/`} class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium border hover:shadow-sm transition-all" style="border-color: #2E75B6; color: #2E75B6; background-color: rgba(46,117,182,0.05);">{area.name}</a>
      ))}
    </div>
    <p class="text-gray-700">Ready to get started? <a href="/contact/" class="font-medium underline" style="color: #2E75B6;">Schedule a free consultation</a> with ProAxis, or explore our <a href="/tax-services/tax-preparation/" class="font-medium underline" style="color: #2E75B6;">tax preparation</a> and <a href="/business-services/bookkeeping/" class="font-medium underline" style="color: #2E75B6;">bookkeeping services</a>.</p>
  </article>

  <TestimonialsSection />
  <CTASection heading={"CPA Services in " + city + ", NJ — Schedule Your Free Consultation"} />
</BaseLayout>
